90f1c838b4ed79af1b","tid":1221796,"uid":101887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77394c51c91f8fbb12ee7f25287237417c0c552c","tid":1221796,"uid":111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3699174194d8e20b0663b42b9fca8634ce36cca3","tid":1221796,"uid":101887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c9ff96723c585e05963aefe465fbd8ec59f6569","tid":1221796,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"感覺上好多法例都係任由法官詮釋 特別係以前從未有過 或者只有極少案例的罪行<br />\n冇民主制衡的情況下<br />\n好多時候只係靠法官自律<br />\n而港共當然用最寬鬆的標準啦<br />\n我想問下有冇其他普通法國家關於暴動罪的案例可以參考下？<br />\n當地的法官點樣詮釋暴動罪？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"睇返呢條條例係1970年制訂，其實大家都知背境係同67暴動有關，當時其實係無所謂民主化嘅野，仍然仲係殖民統治為主，所以司法機關其實有好大權力解釋嘅角色<br />\n香港其實已有暴動案案例，近至2016梁天琦案，遠至越南難民暴動案<br />\n作為開始，我地可以睇番2016旺角暴動罪中控辯雙方提交嘅案例，了解下本港法庭現有對暴動罪嘅詮釋，因為法庭會傾向先翻查本地案例，再考慮其他普通法案例<br />\nR v Caird (1970) 54 Cr App. R. 499 , R v Pilgrim (1983) 5 Cr. App. R. ( S ) 140, AG v Tse Ka Wah (1992) 2 HKCLR 16 , SJ v Cheung Chun Chin (2002) 2 HKLRD 233 (控方提交），R v Tyler (1941)<br />\n判決書：<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/2683/法官沈小民就旺角暴動罪判詞全文\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F2683%2F%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%B2%88%E5%B0%8F%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%B1%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E8%A9%9E%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpEaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=02bd1708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/2683/法官沈小民就旺角暴動罪判詞全文</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestand.news/politics/旺角騷亂案-梁天琦-盧建民-黃家駒判決書全文/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestand.news%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E6%A1%88-%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6-%E7%9B%A7%E5%BB%BA%E6%B0%91-%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%B6%E9%A7%92%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA%E6%9B%B8%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpEaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=48814585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestand.news/